-- both addition and removal of phone numbers in the 'donotcall' table.
-- This SP takes a CSV list of phone numbers and an EmployeeId, and based
-- on the action specified ('add' or 'remove'), it will add new or remove existing
-- phone numbers from the table.
--
-- Example Usage:
-- 1) To add new numbers: EXEC AddRemoveDoNotCall '555-5555,555-5556', 'E123', 'add';
-- 2) To remove numbers: EXEC AddRemoveDoNotCall '555-5555,555-5556', NULL, 'remove';
-- =============================================

